news.title: RHB set to introduce two residential schemes for middle-income groups in Jaipur
news.para: The housing schemes in Mansarovar are meant for two middle-income groups. The two schemes – named Ganga and Gulmohar – will have 160 flats of 2-BHK and 3-BHK categories.

news.title: Ahmedabad civic body extends rebate scheme for property tax payment till May 30
news.para: Between April 8 and 28, the AMC received advance property tax from over 3.95 lakh residents, with a collection of Rs 482.89 crore. The total rebate amounted to Rs 52.78 crore.

news.title: Lucknow: LDA forms committee to address Basant Kunj’s issues
news.para: Officials said that launched in the 1990s, the Basant Kunj scheme covered 1,353 acres spread across ten sectors (A to J), involving land of around 800 farmers and inhabitants
